# Styles

- Edit `src/styles/`, not compiled output.
- Primary entry: `src/styles/main.scss` (imported in `BaseLayout.astro`).
- Vite compiles Sass during `npm run dev` / `npm run build`.
- Legacy root `scss/` and `css/main.css` were removed after Astro migration.
